g.text: Title: ICE40HX4K ICEduino educational breakout board
In the case MAX11614 is not avaible, MAX11615
can be placed. In this case, FB7 must not be placed,
but FB8 instead. Also the I2C levelshifter transistors and
the 5 V pull ups must no be placed.
